<TITLE> Igloo launches new varieties at ice-cream fair </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 2 (bdnews24.com)  Igloo will launch 7 new type's of ice-cream at the "IglooDhaka Sheraton Ice-cream Fair" which starts on Wednesday. This is the third such fair organised by Igloo and will last four days. The fair will continue from 10am to 8pm everyday. With a 500 Taka coupon, visitors will be able to eat ice-cream all day long. bd
